FIRST - TIME FRESHMEN ORIENTATION


 

 
Summer 2023 Orientation for First Year Students!Please check back in the coming weeks for more information about registration for in-person sessions and online modules.
 
First Time First Year Orientation is tentatively scheduled for the month of July, 2023.







Transfer Student Orientation


 

 
Summer 2023 Orientation for Fall Transfer Students!Please check back in the coming weeks for more information about registration for in-person sessions and online modules. 
 
Transfer Orientation is tentatively scheduled for the month of June, 2023.
